-- Qatar Navigation Unit Gets $330 Million in Contracts From Qatar Petroleum
-- B y   R o b e r t   T u t t l e
-- 2010-12-30T07:42:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-30/qatar-navigation-division-wins-330-million-contract-from-qatar-petroleum.html
Qatar Navigation Co., a freight
transportation company, said one of its units won two contracts
valued at 1.2 billion riyals ($330 million) from state-owned
Qatar Petroleum.  Halul Offshore Services Co. will provide specialized
services to the oilfields of Qatar Petroleum, its subsidiaries
and joint ventures, Qatar Navigation said in a statement to
Qatar Exchange today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Robert Tuttle in Doha at 
